      <title>美国就业数据疲软 加拿大央行料将加快降息步伐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/bank-of-canada-seen-cutting-rates-faster-after-weak-us-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国劳动力市场的宽松速度似乎快于预期，市场押注加拿大央行将在今年余下的每次利率决策中降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/bank-of-canada-seen-cutting-rates-faster-after-weak-us-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 19:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
