    <item>
      <title>Byju 的贷款人试图阻止向印度板球委员会付款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/byju-s-lenders-seek-to-block-payment-to-india-cricket-board</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国贷款机构正试图冻结陷入困境的印度教育科技公司 Byju’s 的一名被停职董事的资产，称他的现金应该用来偿还债务，而不是偿还欠印度板球管理委员会的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/byju-s-lenders-seek-to-block-payment-to-india-cricket-board</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 18:52:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Enbridge 寻求批准向土著社区出售股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/enbridge-seeks-approval-to-sell-stake-to-indigenous-communities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Enbridge Inc. 正在寻求监管部门的批准，将其不列颠哥伦比亚省天然气管道系统的部分股份出售给土著群体，这可能预示着这些社区和加拿大能源公司之间将再次建立合作伙伴关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/enbridge-seeks-approval-to-sell-stake-to-indigenous-communities</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 18:52:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗当选后仍坚持掌权，委内瑞拉债券价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/maduro-clings-to-power-crushing-bondholder-hopes-in-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在不到一周的时间里，委内瑞拉的债权人已经从猜测政治转型将把债券价格推高到多高，转而衡量债券价格将下跌多少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/maduro-clings-to-power-crushing-bondholder-hopes-in-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 18:41:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币贷款机构 Genesis 完成重组并开始发放贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/crypto-lender-genesis-completes-restructuring-begins-payouts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币贷款机构 Genesis Global 及其相关公司完成了破产重组，并开始向债权人分配约 40 亿美元的数字资产和现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/crypto-lender-genesis-completes-restructuring-begins-payouts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 18:34:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Fibra Prologis 领跑墨西哥近岸外包之王</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/prologis-emerges-as-top-contender-for-mexico-s-terrafina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普洛斯地产墨西哥公司 (Prologis Property Mexico) 正逐渐成为收购墨西哥最大的工业房地产公司之一的头号竞争者，结束了围绕这一在近岸外包热潮中因其潜力而备受青睐的资产的激烈竞价战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/prologis-emerges-as-top-contender-for-mexico-s-terrafina</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:02:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求担忧压倒战争风险，油价跌至七个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对世界两大经济体需求的担忧盖过了地缘政治风险的加剧，油价跌至近七个月来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 23:31:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：标普 500 指数或将迎来两年来最糟糕的就业形势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[疲软的就业报告引发人们担忧，美联储维持利率在二十年高位的决定可能会导致经济进一步放缓，从而加剧了股市抛售，债券收益率下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
